{"TopicId":164841,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Armless Amy\u0026#039;s Rock Wrestling Challenge","CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-26T19:27:47Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-26T19:27:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAmy Kerman would have been an astronaut. But mishandling of two badly placed girders by \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E staff resulted in poor Amy\u0027s arms being tragically torn off. Amy was sad enough to have lost her arms, but when she found that the Kerbal Space Program wouldn\u0027t accept her into the astronaut corps, she couldn\u0027t be sadder.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo the KSP gave her a chance, if only to keep the astronaut complex from being flooded: Design a mission to collect an asteroid without any \u0022arms\u0022 and they\u0027d let her into the space program.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EYour task: Without using the Advanced Grabbing Unit in any way, bring an asteroid into low orbit around Kerbin.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHard mode:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003ETake the asteroid from Dres orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CairoJack","CreatedById":169033,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-26T22:02:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery cool!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"icantmakemodels","CreatedById":90378,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-26T22:37:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHold my beer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI might get it from Dres because I\u0027m too lazy to wait for a kerbin-intersecting one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-08-27T01:08:40Z\u0022 title=\u002208/27/2017 01:08  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 27, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by icantmakemodels\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-27T04:22:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223158129\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022164841\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221503787078\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002290378\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022icantmakemodels\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, icantmakemodels said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHold my beer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is the second beer I\u0027m holding.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpoiler for thoughts on how I might do this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably a good way to capture an asteroid is some form of cage around the asteroid, which then is closed off by either having a second half dock to it or with some form of extendable part.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"icantmakemodels","CreatedById":90378,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-27T17:50:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA few questions:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(a) Can I use multiple launches?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(b) Can I borrow some \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E thrusters\u00A0from SpaceY?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-08-27T18:21:56Z\u0022 title=\u002208/27/2017 06:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 27, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by icantmakemodels\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}